data.description: Beautiful Country Home located in the Center of Coweta! This home features 4 bedrooms with walk in closets on all rooms and a game/flex room to be used for office/gaming or a 5th bedroom with built in cabinets and closets! Vaulted ceiling in living and game room, open living room with spacious design. Kitchen has been remodeled with white cabinets, granite countertops and opened bar area. Additional room has lots of windows and can be used as a sun room or a formal dining. Home sits on a corner lot with mature trees, above ground pool, shed and privacy fence on 3 sides. Garage has been converted into a workshop with bench, shelving and storage space for all tool working needs. Covered front porch and large patio in the back. Drive to any school in Coweta are less than 8 minutes, Tulsa is a 30 minute drive, this home is a MUST SEE! Please note Garage has been turned into a workshop.
